   <td style="text-align:left;"> Gender nonconforming means not adhering to society's gender norms. People may describe themselves as gender nonconforming if they don't conform to the gender expression, presentation, behaviors, roles, or expectations that society sees as the norm for their gender. ([APA Guidelines - PDF](https://www.apa.org/practice/guidelines/transgender.pdf)) </td>
  </tr>
