   <td style="text-align:left;"> Labelled data (or labelled vectors) is a common data structure in other statistical environments to store meta-information about variables, like variable names, value labels or multiple defined missing values. (<a href="https://strengejacke.github.io/sjlabelled/articles/intro_sjlabelled.html">sjlabelled</a>) </td>
